  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "QC & QA Director",
  "description": "<h3>Maintains product quality by enforcing quality assurance policies and procedures to ensure conformity with HQ specifications, government and industry standards.</h3><h3>Assures Product Quality, production processes, documents maintenance, production environment complied to our strict HQ standards as well as our local Government requirements.</h3><h3>Reviewing the quality standards and production processes from time to time and delivering HQ requirements pertaining to quality issues and quality/product regulatory compliance issues with external partners as well as internal production team and QC team.</h3><h3>Oversees the Workplace Health and Safety issues of the Company. Ensuring regulatory compliance and safe work procedures are instilled in the workplace.</h3><h3>Reporting any workplace accidents/near misses to our Japan HQ.</h3><h3>Responsible for maintaining Company's Food Safety Management System as well as Quality Management System and ensuring its strict compliance.</h3><h3>Negotiate with suppliers on raw materials as well as packaging materials procurement.</h3><h3>Investigate any customers' complaints regarding quality issues together with Production team and QC team.</h3><h3>Explaining and making reports and recommending corrective and preventive actions to our Japan HQ Quality Assurance Department.</h3><h3>Communicate and work closely with our Japan HQ Quality Assurance and Quality Control Management team.</h3><h3>Prepare reports to communicate the outcome of any quality activities to our Japan HQ Quality Assurance Dept.</h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><p></p><p></p>",
